  "scopeRestrictions": {
    "linearAttentionLayers": "named_blocker",
    "linearAttentionLayersDetail": "Qwen 3.6 27B is a hybrid architecture (full + linear attention). Manifest carries both linear_attn.{A_log,conv1d,dt_bias,in_proj_a/b/qkv/z,norm,out_proj} and self_attn.{q,k,v,o}_proj per layer. The TSIR/CSL emit path covers full-attention-only today; linear-attn (Mamba-style SSM with conv1d) has no TSIR body op. This smoke config exercises the full-attention layer pattern; linear-attn layers compile-attempt is a typed-blocker until a SemanticBodyOp.linear_attn body lands.",
    "mropeInterleaved": "named_blocker",
    "mropeInterleavedDetail": "Manifest carries mropeInterleaved=true with mropeSection=[11,11,10] (3D rotary for text/image/video). For text-only inference the smoke config falls back to standard 1D RoPE with partialRotaryFactor=0.25 (num_pairs = headDim * 0.25 / 2 = 32). True mrope lowering is a typed-blocker.",
    "causalAttentionPrefill": "bound",
    "causalAttentionPrefillDetail": "AttentionScoresBody now accepts causal_mode in {.none, .causal, .sliding_window} (emit_kernel_body_attention.zig). Prefill receipts at manifest shape are unblocked from the body-op side; per-PE residency for attn_prefill at head_dim=256 (the 27B kv-axis-sharded redesign) is a separate Doe-gated item.",
    "attentionOutputGate": "bound",
    "attentionOutputGateDetail": "Qwen 3.6 27B applies sigmoid(qGateProjection) * attnOutput before the O projection. The TSIR sigmoid_gated body op, the doe_wgsl classifier surface, and the exec-v1 opToSpec map (with `o_gate` aliased to `sigmoid_gated`) are all wired. The smoke config now declares an explicit `o_gate` step between attention and o_proj that reads (q_proj_output, attention_output) → gated. Receipts surface the gate as a discrete kernel.",
    "swigluFfnFusedGate": "bound",
    "swigluFfnFusedGateDetail": "Qwen FFN is silu(gate_proj(x)) * up_proj(x) → down_proj. The smoke config now declares the activation step as `silu_gated` with inputsFrom=[gate_proj, up_proj]; the TSIR silu_gated body op + classifier + opToSpec + host-plan gated bindings are all wired. Receipts surface the gate as a discrete kernel."
  },
